{
  "message": "feat(overprompting): add page route and social share images\n\nCreate the route structure for /writing/overprompting with proper metadata\nand Satori-safe OG/Twitter share images.\n\nPage (page.tsx):\n- Server component with static metadata\n- Title: \"The Overprompting Trap | Jeffrey Emanuel\"\n- Description summarizing the article's key insight\n- JSON-LD Article schema for SEO\n- No explicit openGraph/twitter metadata (uses file convention)\n- Clean import of OverpromptingArticle client component\n\nOpenGraph image (opengraph-image.tsx, 1200x630):\n- Edge runtime for optimal performance\n- Dark gradient background with warm amber/rose accents\n- Custom funnel SVG visualization representing constraint narrowing\n  - Outer rings, funnel shape, constraint lines\n  - Input dots at top (many), output dot at bottom (single, dim)\n  - X marks for rejected possibilities\n- \"AI Prompting \u2014 Strategy\" category pill\n- Two-line title with gradient text\n- Three tag pills: \"Chef Analogy\", \"Two-Phase\", \"Search Space\"\n- jeffreyemanuel.com domain in corner\n\nTwitter image (twitter-image.tsx, 1200x600):\n- Same visual design as OG, adjusted for Twitter dimensions\n- Slightly smaller typography and spacing\n- Verified non-zero byte response (Satori renders successfully)\n\nSatori compatibility fixes applied:\n- Replaced &apos; HTML entity with JavaScript string literal\n- Removed <g> wrapper, inlined attributes on each <path>\n- display: \"flex\" on all elements\n- Only safe SVG elements: circle, rect, path, line, defs, linearGradient, stop\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
